This repo provides code for a contacts app.
Functionality provided:
-retrieving all contacts from the database
-retrieving more information about a certain contact upon clicking on that contact
-deleting contact
-deleting email from a contact
-adding an email to a contact
-updating contact first and last name
-regex check on emails
-cancelling changes to emails and name.
PS: click on plus icon for new email input field to pop up. Hover next to the 
input field and a minus icon should appear which allows users to remove the input
field in case they don't want to add a new email anymore

Front-end features:
-Fade in and fade out animations
